    <div class="rad-dp-faq-inner">
      <div class="rad-dp-sec-hdr">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions — Denting &amp; Painting Karachi</h2>
        <p>Common questions about car denting and painting services in Karachi</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rad-dp-faq-list">
        <div class="rad-dp-faq-item">
          <div class="rad-dp-faq-q">How long does car denting and painting take in Karachi?<span class="rad-dp-faq-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="rad-dp-faq-a"><p>Minor dent removal takes 1–2 hours. A single panel repaint typically takes 1 day including prep, painting, and curing. Full car repaints take 3–5 working days depending on vehicle size and scope.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="rad-dp-faq-item">
          <div class="rad-dp-faq-q">Can you match my car's exact paint color?<span class="rad-dp-faq-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="rad-dp-faq-a"><p>Yes — we use a computerized spectrophotometer to read your car's exact OEM color code. We then mix the paint to match precisely, so the repainted panel blends seamlessly with the rest of the car. We carry color data for all major makes including Suzuki, Toyota, Honda, KIA, Hyundai, MG, and imported vehicles.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="rad-dp-faq-item">
          <div class="rad-dp-faq-q">What's the difference between PDR and regular dent repair?<span class="rad-dp-faq-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="rad-dp-faq-a"><p>Paintless Dent Repair (PDR) is used for small, shallow dents where the paint is intact — it works by massaging the metal back into shape from behind the panel, without any filler or repainting. Regular dent repair involves filling, sanding, priming, and repainting — used when the paint is cracked, chipped, or the dent is too deep for PDR.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="rad-dp-faq-item">
          <div class="rad-dp-faq-q">Do you offer denting and painting services at home/on-site in Karachi?<span class="rad-dp-faq-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="rad-dp-faq-a"><p>PDR and minor scratch polishing can sometimes be done on-site, but all painting work must be done in our dust-free spray booth to achieve a clean, professional finish. We recommend bringing the vehicle to our studio in Karachi for best results.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="rad-dp-faq-item">
          <div class="rad-dp-faq-q">How much does denting and painting cost in Karachi?<span class="rad-dp-faq-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="rad-dp-faq-a"><p>Costs vary depending on the damage and vehicle size. Minor dent removal starts from PKR 2,500 and a single panel repaint starts from PKR 8,000. Send us a WhatsApp photo of the damage for a quick, free estimate.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="rad-dp-faq-item">
          <div class="rad-dp-faq-q">Which areas of Karachi do you serve?<span class="rad-dp-faq-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="rad-dp-faq-a"><p>We serve customers from all areas of Karachi including DHA, Clifton, Gulshan-e-Iqbal, North Karachi, Federal B Area, Nazimabad, PECHS, Bahadurabad, Gulistan-e-Johar, Saddar, and surrounding areas.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
